<plot>This film is based on an actor who suffers from an identity crisis with his film noir private detective character, 'The Mole' (his character actually wears a facial mole). In this insane paradoxical world, everything is superficial - just as is a facial mole and the 'No Mole, No Role' syndrome! We exaggerate the same as you experience the cruel fist of fate for all actors - like toothpaste, they get squeezed out and replaced with a new tube. So we now reside in a film noir world where alter egos take over. A private detective is obsessed with a case of mistaken identity. He is in love with a virgin who has been kidnapped by the evil mob boss and his henchman. The bad guys scheme to get rid of the private dick by hiring an assassin to take care of him. At the same time, a mysterious man lurks in the shadows, watching his every move. Racing against time, the private dick has to rescue the love of his life and get out of this filthy town.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?577147</url></doc>
